              "action": "close"
            }
          ]
        },
        "team_help": {
          "id": "team_help",
          "trigger": "interaction",
          "lines": [
            "Hire for culture fit AND skills. Both matter equally.",
            "Your first 10 hires define your company culture forever.",
            "Equity is currency when you can't pay market salaries.",
            "Don't hire too fast - every bad hire costs months of progress.",
            "Great people want to work with other great people. Bar raises itself.",
            "Culture isn't ping pong tables - it's how you treat people when things go wrong!"
          ],
          "repeatable": true,
          "choices": [
            {
              "text": "Let's build this team!",
